resources.string:
Restore the system: the use of Microsofts official ESD files to achieve Windows system recovery, the main operations are:
    1. Click the Restore System button at the bottom of the screen to bring up the User Selection dialog box.; 
    2. Select the normal user;
    Warning: At this point can not carry out other operations - including shutdown and other dangerous action;
    After the progress is complete, the system is restored

Configuration information, custom APP default information, the main operations are:
    1. wim file: the location of the custom input ESD file; 
    2. Download address: Custom input ESD file download URL;
    3. Command line: Execute shell command
    Click the "Save" button and store it in the configuration file
